'''Rustam Ashurmatov''' ({{Langx|uz-Cyrl|Рустам Ашурматов}}; born 7 July 1996), sometimes spelt as '''Rustamjon Ashurmatov''', is an Uzbek footballer who plays as a [[Defender (association football)|defender]] for Iranian club [[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=ثبت‌ نام 10 هزار نفر در جشنواره ملی ملکوت |url=https://www.isna.ir/xdtjwp |access-date=2025-07-09 |website=www.isna.ir |date=24 November 2013 |archive-date=9 July 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20250709111746/https://www.isna.ir/xdTJwp |url-status=live }}</ref>

==Career==
===Club===
On 7 February 2019, [[FC Bunyodkor]] announced that Ashurmatov had joined [[Gwangju FC|Gwangju]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Рустам Ашурматовга омад тилаймиз! |url=https://t.me/bunyodkor_club/4853 |website=t.me/ |publisher=FC Bunyodkor Telegram |accessdate=26 February 2019 |language=Uzbek |date=7 February 2019 |archive-date=27 February 2019 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227060346/https://t.me/bunyodkor_club/4853 |url-status=live }}</ref>

On 19 January 2021, [[Gangwon FC]] announced that Ashurmatov had joined [[Gangwon FC|Gangwon]].<ref>{{cite web |title=[오피셜] 강원FC '우즈벡 국대' 아슐마토프 영입 |url=https://m.sports.naver.com/kfootball/article/216/0000111285|work=Goal.com|via=Naver|accessdate=19 January 2021 |language=Korean |date=19 January 2021 |archive-date=11 November 2023 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20231111110238/https://n.news.naver.com/sports/kfootball/article/216/0000111285 |url-status=live }}</ref> Gangwon announced that Ashurmatov left the club on 15 February 2022.<ref>{{cite press release|publisher=[[Gangwon FC|Gangwon]]|url=https://www.facebook.com/gangwonfc/posts/5090870527695189|title=지난 시즌 입단해 강원에서 멋진 활약을 보여준|date=15 February 2022|access-date=15 February 2022|language=ko|archive-date=17 November 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20231117085445/https://www.facebook.com/gangwonfc/posts/5090870527695189|url-status=live}}</ref>

On 18 February 2022, Ashurmatov signed with [[PFC Navbahor Namangan|Navbahor Namangan]].<ref>{{cite press release|publisher=[[PFC Navbahor Namangan|Navbahor Namangan]]|url=https://www.pfcnavbahor.uz/index.php/uz/yangiliklar/klub-yangiliklari/3363-rustam-ashurmatov-zhamoamiz-bilan-shartnoma-imzoladi|title=Рустам Ашурматов жамоамиз билан шартнома имзолади|date=18 February 2022|access-date=18 February 2022|language=uz|archive-date=30 November 2024|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20241130201209/https://www.pfcnavbahor.uz/index.php/uz/yangiliklar/klub-yangiliklari/3363-rustam-ashurmatov-zhamoamiz-bilan-shartnoma-imzoladi|url-status=live}}</ref>

On 14 January 2023, Ashurmatov joined [[FC Rubin Kazan]] in Russia on a 3.5-year contract.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=FC Rubin Kazan|url=https://www.rubin-kazan.ru/posts/rustam-ashurmatov-igrok-rubina|title=РУСТАМ АШУРМАТОВ – ИГРОК "РУБИНА"|date=14 January 2023|language=ru|access-date=16 January 2023|archive-date=11 August 2023|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20230811091720/https://www.rubin-kazan.ru/posts/rustam-ashurmatov-igrok-rubina|url-status=live}}</ref>

On 9 July 2025, Ashurmatov joined [[Esteghlal F.C.|Esteghlal]] in Iran on a 2-year contract.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2025-07-09 |title=رسمی؛ رستم آشورماتوف به استقلال پیوست |url=https://www.tarafdari.com/node/2642479 |access-date=2025-07-09 |website=طرفداری |language=fa |archive-date=31 December 2025 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20251231135139/https://www.tarafdari.com/node/2642479 |url-status=live }}</ref>

===International===
A player for the [[Uzbekistan national football team]] since 2017, Ashurmatov has also have played for the Uzbekistan national youth teams in international tournaments such as [[2013 FIFA U-17 World Cup]], [[2015 FIFA U-20 World Cup]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/fifa-tournaments/players-coaches/people=371415/index.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150907003217/http://www.fifa.com/fifa-tournaments/players-coaches/people=371415/index.html|url-status=dead|archive-date=September 7, 2015|title=FIFA Tournaments - Players & Coaches - Rustamjon ASHURMATOV|website=FIFA.com|accessdate=21 June 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/u17worldcup/matches/round=259263/match=300253593/match-report.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331191639/http://www.fifa.com/u17worldcup/matches/round=259263/match=300253593/match-report.html|url-status=dead|archive-date=March 31, 2016|title=FIFA U-17 World Cup UAE 2013 - Matches - Panama-Uzbekistan|website=FIFA.com|accessdate=21 June 2018}}</ref> and [[2018 AFC U-23 Championship]], in which he would win the latter tournament with [[Uzbekistan national under-23 football team]], with him scoring in the final.

